text: Hello 2nd roomie, wing me apan hi dono reh gye the shayad jo 2nd year me bhi double room me rahe, par maza aaya, yaad h chhipkali bhagane ke liye kitni mehnat ki thi. Aur haan, F-312 tha room 314 nahi. Itne saare tissue paper rakhe the room me bhai ne, ab batane ki zaroorat nahi h kyon. Acha laga tera dedication dekh ke teri girlfriend ke liye, sab kuch manage kr liya cpi bhi bandi bhi projects bhi aur ab double major bhi kar rha, chaapu to h bhai apna. Aise hi success milti rahe, kabhi raaste takraye to baki baatein karenge.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Kamboj ka bahut dhanyawaad ki usne aap jaise mahaan mahapurush se hamari dosti karwayi. Launda apna hamesha se hi stud rha h, bhai ko bandi ne khud approach kiya, kitno ko to reject kr chuka h ye. Daudhta bhi acha h, bas bhaag ke shaadi mat kar liyo. Apna work from home wala plan yaad h na, chalna h bc, pahado se kaam karenge. Jitna bhi waqt tere saath bitaya bahut maza aaya, bahut hase. Aage se koi sundar ladki dikhe to hame bhi dikhana zoo jaisa kaand mat karna, bata dena chahiye tha yaar, aaj tak mujhe regret hota h usse dekh nhi paaya. Khair apan to milne hi waale hain, agar work from home wala plan work nahi kara to trip pe chalenge bc.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Thank you bhai subah uthane ke liye, mujhe pata h meri deep sleep ki wajah se kitna pareshaan hua h tu, sorry uske liye. Aise hi chaapte raho, mera aashirwaad hamesha tumhare saath h.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Ham dono ki dosti ka to saare college ko hi pata hai. I was amazed to see how two completely opposite personalities (one a shy introvert and the other an extrovert, ab batane ki zarurat nahi h kaun kya h) can be great friends. Thank you hamesha time se hospital pahuchane ke liye. 4 Saal saare kaand/kaam ikhatte hi kare hain, kitni yaadein, likhne baithun to jagah kam padh jaaye, ginne baithun to ginti khatam ho jaaye. Ab kya hi likhu, memoir unke likhe jaate hain jinke saath aage memories na banni ho, apan to milte rahenge yaar, chandigarh aa rha hun main bc. Milke college ke din yaad karenge. Aur haan, I am the real Beard Man, he is the fake one.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Ham dono ki dosti ka to saare college ko hi pata hai. I was amazed to see how two completely opposite personalities (one a shy introvert and the other an extrovert, ab batane ki zarurat nahi h kaun kya h) can be great friends. Meri zindagi me bahut kam log hain jinko main dost bolta hun, he is one of them, so you can always rely on him, bhai thank you college ke 4 saal yaadgaar banane ke liye yaar. Thank you hamesha time se hospital pahuchane ke liye. Thank you antaragni me help karne ke liye, main hi chutiya tha jo baat nahi kar paaya. Teri favourite line "Bai bahut kamm peya hoya mere kol, bund paati payi aa", aur wo tu aaj bhi use krta hai, aur probably zindagi bhar karega, kheech kheech ke antaragni me le jana padhta tha. 4 Saal saare kaand/kaam ikhatte hi kare hain, kitni yaadein, likhne baithun to jagah kam padh jaaye, ginne baithun to ginti khatam ho jaaye. Ab kya hi likhu, memoir unke likhe jaate hain jinke saath aage memories na banni ho, apan to milte rahenge yaar, chandigarh aa rha hun main bc. Milke college ke din yaad karenge. Snapchat me random ladkiyon ko add krna band krde ganda kat skta h. 22/04/2023 ka target h mera, aaunga teri ek month ki salary lene bc. Aur haan, I am the real Beard Man, he is the fake one.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Lambora sahab, gaon se aaya hua launda har jagah chaap rha h chahe wo sports ho padhai ho ya kuch bhi. I liked your helping nature, jab mera phone paani me gir gaya tab tune hi apna keypad wala phone diya tha, maine kaha tha party le liyo, par li hi nahi tune aaj tak. Kafi disciplined tha tu, aur ye cheez tujhe aur bhi aage tak leke jaaegi. Kaafi positive vibes aati thi tujhse, and I wish you all the happiness in life.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Aur samu boi, kaafi suljha hua banda laga yaar tu, bahut kuch seekha tere se, I hope that we would have known each other better, khair kabhi mauka mila to zarur, baaki aise hi chaapte raho. Uss din raat me kisse baat kr rha tha bataya nahi yaar tune.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Ethe ethe ethe ethe. Aur sandy bete, ab mess ke liye kaun uthaega tujhe, subah dopahar raat hamesha sota hi rehta tha. Tere saath acche topics pe discussion krke maza aata tha yaar, tera perspective jaan ke. Jab apna room aamne saamne hua, maza hi aane laga, kaisi kaisi baatein kari apan ne soch ke bhi hasi aati h, mess me kamboj ka kutiya aur ladki wala topic yaad h, usko kitna mushkil ho gya tha convince krna hi kutta kutiya ki paas hi jayega. Khair, I will always have your back, kabhi bhi kuch bhi zaroorat ho. Country ka future finance minister hai tu, tere se to connected rehna hi padhega. Apni planned trip yaad h na, chalna h bc, shayad thode college ke experiences relive kar lein. Bhai discord chalana sikha de yaar, bahut achi angrezi seekh li h tune.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Bhai tera shaant swabhav bahut sahi lagta tha yaar, hamesha smile krta rehta tha. Har nashe ke baad bhai ne bahut ultiyan kari h, ham jaise sober logo ko sambhalna padhta tha. Aise hi khush reh hamesha.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Bhai ne akhri sem me har tareeke ka nasha try kr liya. Kota waali story mast thi yaar, puri movie ban sakti h uske upar. Baki khush raho abad raho, milenge kabhi.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja

text: Acha lagta h jab tum jaise chaapu log madhya pradesh ka naam roshan karte ho, kaafi disciplined tha bhai tu, time se sona, time se uthna. Baki baat krne ka saleeka bhi acha tha tera. Khair, ab kanpur se bhopal ki train to nahi, par bhopal se bangalore ki flight me ikhatte chalenge. Bangalore me party krte hain, milte hain.
author: Gurpreet Singh Tuteja
